ygData.messageBody:
Trueshot trivial level is over 200 that may be
why it failed. Tho it is possible to get it at lower
skill, it is more likely at or over 200.<br>I found a
good site that discusses bow and arrow trivials and
has a table down the bottom which will tell you what
arrow to make at what level to increase your skill
while also getting usable product and not wasting too
much
money.<br><a href=http://members.bellatlantic.net/~ewj/fletchguide/index.htm target=new>http://members.bellatlantic.net/~ewj/fletchguide/index.htm</a><br><br>Good Luck and don't give up on the Trueshot you need
it.<br><br>Bebinn<br>15 Ranger Woodelf on Bristlebane Server
